position":4,"arabic":"بِسْمِ","translation":"সহ নাম","audioUrl":"wbw/011_041_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42429,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/011_041_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42430,"position":6,"arabic":"مَجْر۪ىٰهَا","translation":"তার গতি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_041_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42431,"position":7,"arabic":"وَمُرْسَىٰهَآ ۚ","translation":"ও তার স্থিতি","audioUrl":"wbw/011_041_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42433,"position":8,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/011_041_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42434,"position":9,"arabic":"رَبِّى","translation":"আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/011_041_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42435,"position":10,"arabic":"لَغَفُورٌۭ","translation":"অবশ্যই ক্ষমাশীল","audioUrl":"wbw/011_041_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42436,"position":11,"arabic":"رَّحِيمٌۭ","translation":"পরম দয়ালু\"","audioUrl":"wbw/011_041_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42437,"position":12,"arabic":"٤١","translation":"(৪১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":42,"arabic":"وَهِىَ تَجْرِى بِهِمْ فِى مَوْجٍۢ كَٱلْجِبَالِ وَنَادَىٰ نُوحٌ ٱبْنَهُۥ وَكَانَ فِى مَعْزِلٍۢ يَٰبُنَىَّ ٱرْكَب مَّعَنَا وَلَا تَكُن مَّعَ ٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ","translation":"And it moved on with them into waves that were like mountains. At that [moment] Noah cried out to a son of his, who had kept himself aloof [from the others]: \"O my dear son! Embark with us, and remain not with those who deny the truth!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1515.mp3","surahId":11,"words":[{"id":43113,"position":1,"arabic":"وَهِىَ","translation":"এবং তা","audioUrl":"wbw/011_042_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43114,"position":2,"arabic":"تَجْرِى","translation":"বয়ে চলে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_042_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43115,"position":3,"arabic":"بِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের নিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/011_042_003.mp3","charTypeNa